00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,110
昨天
yesterday.

748
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:36,210
呣，既然你昨天搬进他那里
Mmm, and since yesterday, you've moved in with him

749
00:36:36,220 --> 00:36:38,310
现在你俩就一起查案
and now you're solving crimes together.

750
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:41,730
也许我们可以期待到周末有个订婚喜讯？
Might we expect a happy announcement by the end of the week?

751
00:36:41,750 --> 00:36:44,450
- 你是谁？  - 利害相关方罢了
- Who are you? - An interested party.

752
00:36:44,460 --> 00:36:46,270
与夏洛克相关？为何？
Interested in Sherlock? Why?

753
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:48,230
我猜你们不是朋友
I'm guessing you're not friends.

754
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:51,950
你见过他了，你能想象他有几个朋友？
You've met him. How many friends do you imagine he has?

755
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:56,770
我是夏洛克·福尔摩斯所能拥有的，最接近于“朋友”的东西
I am the closest thing to a friend that Sherlock Holmes is capable of having.

756
00:36:56,780 --> 00:36:57,370
那是啥？
And what's that?

757
00:36:57,380 --> 00:36:58,430
- 一个敌人  - 一个敌人？
- An enemy. - An enemy?

758
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,700
当然，是他心目中的
In his mind, certainly.

759
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:04,230
如果你去问他，他可能会说是他的死敌
If you were to ask him, he'd probably say his arch-enemy.

760
00:37:04,750 --> 00:37:06,410
他确实爱搞戏剧化
He does love to be dramatic.

761
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,950
谢谢老天，你倒不戏剧化
Well, thank God you're above all that

762
00:37:15,250 --> 00:37:17,100
希望我没有让你分心
I hope I'm not distracting you.

763
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:19,710
完全没有让我分心
Not distracting me at all.

764
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:22,700
你计划继续与夏洛克·福尔摩斯交往吗？
Do you plan to continue your association with Sherlock Holmes?

765
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:23,970
我可能说错了
I could be wrong...

766
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:26,410
但是…我认为这不是你操心的事
but I think that's none of your business.

767
00:37:26,420 --> 00:37:28,990
- 可能是  - 真的不可能
