警察  开门
Police! Open her up.

1043
00:54:01,870 --> 00:54:02,430
终点

1044
00:54:06,980 --> 00:54:08,000
不
No...

1045
00:54:08,350 --> 00:54:10,390
牙齿，晒黑，怎么，加州人吗
Teeth, tan. What, Californian?

1046
00:54:11,530 --> 00:54:14,200
洛杉矶圣莫尼卡  刚到
LA, Santa Monica. Just arrived.

1047
00:54:14,210 --> 00:54:16,110
- 你怎么可能知道？  - 行李牌
- How could you possibly know that? - The luggage.

1048
00:54:18,080 --> 00:54:19,700
你是第一次来伦敦，对吧
First trip to London, right?

1049
00:54:20,170 --> 00:54:23,030
让的哥载着你四处找目的地吧
Going by your final destination and the cabbie's taking you?

1050
00:54:23,320 --> 00:54:25,100
抱歉，你们是警察吗？
Sorry, are you guys the police?

1051
00:54:25,140 --> 00:54:27,310
对，一切还好吧？
Yeah. Everything all right?

1052
00:54:28,470 --> 00:54:29,340
好
Yeah.

1053
00:54:30,760 --> 00:54:32,310
欢迎来到伦敦
Welcome to London.

1054
00:54:34,280 --> 00:54:36,430
有任何问题，就知会我们
Er, any problems, just let us know.

1055
00:54:40,700 --> 00:54:42,750
基本上只是一辆碰巧慢下来的出租车
Basically just a cab that happened to slow down.

1056
00:54:42,760 --> 00:54:44,310
- 基本上  - 不是那凶手
- Basically. - Not the murderer.

1057
00:54:44,320 --> 00:54:47,630
- 不是那凶手，不是  - 国家不对 很好的不在现场证明
- Not the murderer, no. - Wrong country, good alibi.

1058
00:54:47,830 --> 00:54:49,910
- 他们走了  - 你从哪弄来的这个
- As they go. - Hey, where did you get this?

1059
00:54:51,170 --> 00:54:53,270
- 雷斯垂德探长？  - 对
- Detective Inspector Lestrade? - Yeah.

1060
00:54:53,320 --> 00:54:55,250
他一烦人我就掏他口袋
I pickpocket him when he's annoying.

1061
00:54:55,600 --> 00:54:57,510
你留着那个，我还有很多在公寓里
You can keep that one, I've got plenty at the flat.

1062
00:55:00,650 --> 00:55:01,130
什么？
What?

1063
00:55:01,140 --> 00:55:03,230
没什么，只是…“欢迎来到伦敦”
Nothing, just..."Welcome to London."

1064
00:55:07,040 --> 00:55:09,870
- 气喘上来了吗？  - 随时都可以
- Got your breath back? - Ready when you are.

1065
00:55:19,210 --> 00:55:20,710
这真荒唐
That was ridiculous.

1066
00:55:21,200 --> 00:55:24,230
这是我干过最荒唐的事，有生以来
That was the most ridiculous thing... I've ever done.

1067
00:55:24,550 --> 00:55:26,650
你可是入侵过阿富汗的
And you invaded Afghanistan.

1068
00:55:29,100 --> 00:55:30,530
那可不止我一个
That wasn't just me.

1069
00:55:30,900 --> 00:55:32,230
我们为何不回餐厅？
Why aren't we back at the restaurant?

1070
00:55:32,320 --> 00:55:34,020
他们会盯着的
They can keep an eye out.

1071
00:55:34,720 --> 00:55:36,540
反正机会不大
It was a long shot anyway.

1072
00:55:36,730 --> 00:55:38,470
那我们刚才去那里干嘛？
So what were we doing there?

1073
00:55:41,600 --> 00:55:42,990
只是打发时间
Oh, just passing the time.

1074
00:55:44,070 --> 00:55:45,670
还证明一个观点
And proving a point.

1075
00:55:45,880 --> 00:55:47,230
- 什么观点？  - 你
- What point? - You.

1076
00:55:47,320 --> 00:55:51,440
哈德森太太，华生医生要楼上的房间
Mrs Hudson! Dr Watson willtake the room upstairs.

1077
00:55:51,460 --> 00:55:52,750
谁说的？
Says who?

1078
00:55:53,000 --> 00:55:54,390
门外的人说的
Says the man at the door.

1079
00:56:05,240 --> 00:56:06,510
夏洛克发短信给我
Sherlock texted me.

1080
00:56:07,320 --> 00:56:09,310
他说你忘了这个
He said you forgot this.

1081
00:56:13,600 --> 00:56:14,730
谢谢你
Er, thank you.

1082
00:56:14,850 --> 00:56:15,670
谢谢你
Thank you.

1083
00:56:16,840 --> 00:56:18,670
夏洛克，你干了什么？
Sherlock, what have you done?

1084
00:56:18,760 --> 00:56:20,910
- 哈德森太太？  - 楼上
- Mrs Hudson? - Upstairs.

1085
00:56:26,920 --> 00:56:27,870
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

1086
00:56:27,880 --> 00:56:29,890
我就知道你找到了箱子，我不笨
I knew you'd find the case, I'm not stupid.

1087
00:56:29,940 --> 00:56:31,370
你不能闯进我的公寓
You can't just break into my flat.

1088
00:56:31,410 --> 00:56:34,130
你不能擅留证据，况且我没闯进你的公寓
You can't withhold evidence - and I didn't break into your flat.

1089
00:56:34,140 --> 00:56:35,310
那你把这叫做什么？
What do you call this, then?

1090
00:56:36,300 --> 00:56:37,630
这是一次缉毒行动
It's a drugs bust.

1091
00:56:37,660 --> 00:56:40,030
你认真的？这个人 瘾君子？
Seriously? This guy - a junkie?

1092
00:56:40,080 --> 00:56:41,990
- 你还不了解他吗？  - 约翰
- Have you met him? - John...

1093
00:56:42,130 --> 00:56:43,970
我敢肯定你可以在这公寓搜查一天
I'm pretty sure you could search this flat all day,

1094
00:56:43,980 --> 00:56:46,120
也绝不会找到任何称得上娱乐消遣的东西
you wouldn't find anything you could call recreational.

1095
00:56:46,130 --> 00:56:48,670
- 约翰，你也许该闭嘴了  - 但是这…
- John, you probably want to shut up now. - But come on...

1096
00:56:50,600 --> 00:56:51,910
- 不…  - 什么？
- No... - What?

1097
00:56:52,500 --> 00:56:54,070
- 你？  - 闭嘴
- You? - Shut up!

1098
00:56:54,160 --> 00:56:56,870
- 我不是你的缉毒犬  - 不  安德森是我的缉毒犬
- I'm not your sniffer dog. - No, Anderson's my sniffer dog.

1099
00:56:58,850 --> 00:57:01,270
安德森，缉毒行动与你何干？
Anderson, what are you doing here on a drugs bust?

1100
00:57:01,360 --> 00:57:02,560
我自愿来的
Oh, I volunteered.

1101
00:57:02,570 --> 00:57:05,420
他们都是自愿的，他们严格来说不是缉毒组的
They all did. They're not strictly speaking on the drug squad,

1102
00:57:05,430 --> 00:57:06,110
但他们很敏锐
but they're very keen.

1103
00:57:06,200 --> 00:57:08,220
- 这些是人眼睛吗？  - 放回去
- Are these human eyes? - Put those back!

1104
00:57:08,230 --> 00:57:10,510
- 它们在微波炉里  - 是个实验
- They were in the microwave. - It's an experiment.

1105
00:57:10,600 --> 00:57:11,950
继续搜，伙计们
Keep looking, guys.

1106
00:57:12,040 --> 00:57:14,410
或者你可以用适当的方式帮我们，我就让他们停下
Or you could help us properly, and I'll stand them down.

1107
00:57:14,420 --> 00:57:16,390
- 这真幼稚  - 对，我在跟个孩子打交道
- This is childish. - Well, I'm dealing with a child.

1108
00:57:16,480 --> 00:57:17,770
夏洛克，这是我们的案件
Sherlock, this is ourcase.

1109
00:57:17,780 --> 00:57:20,530
我让你参与，但你不能走开自己干
I'm letting you in, but you do not go off on your own.

1110
00:57:20,850 --> 00:57:21,430
清楚了吗
Clear?

1111
00:57:21,440 --> 00:57:24,720
否则怎样？所以你就设个假缉毒行动来欺压我？
Or what? So you set up a pretend drugs bust to bully me?

1112
00:57:24,730 --> 00:57:26,470
要是找到什么，就不是假的了
It stops being pretend if we find anything.

1113
00:57:26,560 --> 00:57:27,950
我是清白的
I am clean!

1114
00:57:28,040 --> 00:57:32,130
- 你的公寓呢？整个公寓？  - 我连烟都不抽
- Is your flat? All of it? - I don't even smoke.

1115
00:57:32,620 --> 00:57:34,410
我也不抽
Neither do I.

1116
00:57:36,270 --> 00:57:37,910
我们合作吧
So let's work together.

1117
00:57:38,980 --> 00:57:40,970
- 我们找到了瑞琪儿  - 她是谁？
- We've found Rachel. - Who is she?

1118
00:57:41,120 --> 00:57:42,580
詹妮弗·威尔逊的独女
Jennifer Wilson's only daughter.

1119
00:57:42,600 --> 00:57:43,800
她女儿？
Her daughter?

1120
00:57:44,400 --> 00:57:46,780
她为何写下女儿的名字？为什么？
Why would she write her daughter's name? Why?

1121
00:57:46,800 --> 00:57:48,960
管她呢  我们找到了箱子
Never mind that, we found the case.

1122
00:57:48,970 --> 00:57:51,310
据某人说，凶手拿着箱子
According to someone, the murderer has the case,

1123
00:57:51,400 --> 00:57:54,260
而我们发现它在我们最喜欢的精神病人手里
and we found it in the hands of our favourite psychopath.

1124
00:57:54,300 --> 00:57:55,410
不是精神病人，安德森
Not a psychopath, Andersen.

1125
00:57:55,420 --> 00:57:57,510
我是高智商反社会人格，做好调查
I'm a high-functioning sociopath. Do your research.

1126
00:57:57,800 --> 00:58:00,320
你需要带瑞琪儿来问询，我要问她
You need to bring Rachel in to question her. I need to question her.

1127
00:58:00,900 --> 00:58:02,450
- 她死了   - 好极了，如何，何时以及为何？
- She's dead. - Excellent. How, when and why?

1128
00:58:02,460 --> 00:58:03,750
是否有联系？一定有
Is there a connection? There has to be.

1129
00:58:03,900 --> 00:58:06,230
哦，我很怀疑，因为她已死了14年
Well, I doubt it, since she's been dead for 14 years.

1130
00:58:06,320 --> 00:58:07,600
严格来说 她从未活过
Technically, she was never alive.

1131
00:58:08,520 --> 00:58:12,750
瑞琪儿是詹妮弗·威尔逊的死胎女儿，14年前
Rachel was Jennifer Wilson's stillborn daughter, 14 years ago.

1132
00:58:13,400 --> 00:58:14,510
哦  那
Oh, that's...

1133
00:58:15,470 --> 00:58:17,350
那不对，怎么…
...that's not right. How...

1134
00:58:17,700 --> 00:58:19,190
她为何那么做？为什么？
Why would she do that? Why?

1135
00:58:19,550 --> 00:58:21,650
她为什么临死一刻想到女儿？
Why would she think of her daughter in her last moments?

1136
00:58:21,690 --> 00:58:23,890
是啊，反社会，这下我看到了
Yep - sociopath, I'm seeing it now.

1137
00:58:23,900 --> 00:58:25,390
她不是在想自己的女儿
She didn't think about her daughter.

1138
00:58:25,480 --> 00:58:28,780
她刻出这个名字，在地板上，用指甲
She scratched her name on the floor with her fingernails.

1139
00:58:28,800 --> 00:58:31,000
她快死了，这很费劲，会很痛苦
She was dying. It took effort, it would have hurt.

1140
00:58:32,000 --> 00:58:34,580
你说过受害人都是自行服毒
You said that the victims all took the poison themselves,

1141
00:58:34,600 --> 00:58:36,670
他让他们服毒的
that he makes them take it.

1142
00:58:36,760 --> 00:58:39,350
也许他...我不知道...跟他们说了什么
Well, maybe he...I don't know, talks to them.

1143
00:58:39,370 --> 00:58:41,780
也许他以某种方式利用了她女儿的死
Maybe he used the death of her daughter somehow.

1144
00:58:41,790 --> 00:58:44,020
可那是陈年旧事了，她为何还会心烦？
But that was ages ago. Why would she still be upset?

1145
00:58:48,600 --> 00:58:49,110
不好吗？
Not good?

1146
00:58:50,200 --> 00:58:51,150
有点不好，对
Bit not good, yeah.

1147
00:58:51,600 --> 00:58:53,740
如果你快死了  如果你被人谋杀
If you were dying, if you'd been murdered,

1148
00:58:53,750 --> 00:58:55,470
在你最后那几分钟里 你会说什么？
in your very last few seconds, what would you say?

1149
00:58:56,020 --> 00:58:58,390
- “求你，主啊，让我活着”  - 运用你的想象力
- "Please, God, let me live." - Use your imagination!

1150
00:58:59,200 --> 00:58:59,990
我没必要
I don't have to.

1151
00:59:01,400 --> 00:59:03,250
对，但如果你很聪明呢，真的很聪明
Yeah, but if you were clever, really clever.

1152
00:59:03,260 --> 00:59:05,570
詹妮弗·威尔逊操纵那么多情人，她很聪明
Jennifer Wilson running all those lovers - she was clever.

1153
00:59:05,600 --> 00:59:07,230
她是想告诉我们什么
She's trying to tell us something.

1154
00:59:07,320 --> 00:59:09,730
不是门铃在响吗？你的出租车来了，夏洛克
Isn't the doorbell working? Your taxi's here, Sherlock.

1155
00:59:09,740 --> 00:59:11,360
我没叫出租车，走开
I didn't order a taxi. Go away.

1156
00:59:11,370 --> 00:59:13,490
哦，亲爱的 他们弄得真乱
Oh, dear. They're making such a mess.

1157
00:59:13,500 --> 00:59:16,110
- 他们在找什么？ - 这是缉毒行动，哈德森夫人
- What are they looking for? - It's a drugs bust, Mrs Hudson.

1158
00:59:16,400 --> 00:59:19,100
但那些只是治疗我臀部的，是草药…
But they're just for my hip. They're herbal soothers...

1159
00:59:19,110 --> 00:59:22,340
闭嘴，所有人闭嘴！别动，别说话，别呼吸
Shut up, everybody shut up! Don't move, don't speak, don't breathe.

1160
00:59:22,350 --> 00:59:24,650
我在设法思考！安德森转过脸去，你碍到我了
I'm trying to think. Anderson, face the other way. You're putting me off.

1161
00:59:24,800 --> 00:59:27,390
- 什么？我的脸...  - 大家保持安静
- What? My face is - Everybody quiet and still.

1162
00:59:27,400 --> 00:59:29,650
- 安德森，转过背去  - 老天在上
- Anderson, turn your back. - Oh, for God's sake!

1163
00:59:29,670 --> 00:59:31,380
转过去，马上，拜托
Your back, now, please!

1164
00:59:31,400 --> 00:59:33,530
- 来吧 快思考  - 你的出租车怎么办？
- Come on, think. Quick! - What about your taxi?

1165
00:59:33,800 --> 00:59:34,700
哈德森夫人
Mrs Hudson!

1166
00:59:41,240 --> 00:59:44,710
她真聪明 聪明 没错
She was clever. Clever, yes!

1167
00:59:44,800 --> 00:59:47,870
她比你们都聪明，可她死了
She's cleverer than you lot and she's dead.

1168
00:59:47,880 --> 00:59:49,150
你们明白了吗 你们搞懂没？
Do you see? Do you get it?

1169
00:59:49,400 --> 00:59:52,810
她没有丢失手机，她根本没丢，她安插给他的
She didn't lose her phone, she never lost it. She planted it on him.

1170
00:59:52,960 --> 00:59:54,000
当她下车的时候
When she got out of the car,

1171
00:59:54,200 --> 00:59:55,750
她知道她要死了
she knew that she was going to her death.

1172
00:59:55,840 --> 00:59:59,060
她留下手机，是为了引导我们找到凶手
She left the phone in order to lead us to her killer.

1173
00:59:59,100 --> 01:00:02,790
- 但怎么找？  - 你说什么怎么找？
- But how? - What do you mean, how?

1174
01:00:03,300 --> 01:00:04,510
瑞琪儿
Rachel!

1175
01:00:05,950 --> 01:00:07,390
还不明白吗？瑞琪儿
Don't you see? Rachel!

1176
01:00:11,480 --> 01:00:13,320
瞧瞧你们，全都那么茫然
Look at you lot. You're all so vacant.

1177
01:00:13,410 --> 01:00:15,620
不当我是不是很好？一定很放松吧
Is it nice not being me? It must be so relaxing.

1178
01:00:15,620 --> 01:00:17,850
- 瑞琪儿不是人名  - 那它是什么？
- Rachel is not a name. - Then what is it?

1179
01:00:18,300 --> 01:00:19,860
约翰，箱子上有个名牌
John, on the luggage, there's a label.

1180
01:00:19,870 --> 01:00:21,310
电邮地址
E-mail address.

1181
01:00:23,400 --> 01:00:26,830
jennie.pink@mephone.org.uk
Er, jenny.Pink@mephone.Org.Uk.

1182
01:00:26,870 --> 01:00:28,730
噢，我反应太慢了，她没有笔记本电脑
Ah, I've been too slow. She didn't have a laptop,

1183
01:00:28,840 --> 01:00:30,350
说明她是用手机谈生意
which means she did her business on her phone.

1184
01:00:30,440 --> 01:00:32,190
所以是智能手机，能使用电邮
So it's a smartphone, it's e-mail enabled.

1185
01:00:32,280 --> 01:00:33,830
所以有个网页能登她的账户
So there was a website for her account.

1186
01:00:33,920 --> 01:00:35,410
用户名是她的电邮地址
The username is her e-mail address,

1187
01:00:35,420 --> 01:00:37,140
都齐了，现在密码是...
and all together now, the password is...?

1188
01:00:37,600 --> 01:00:40,370
- 瑞琪儿  - 我们能读她的邮件，那又如何？
- Rachel. - So we can read her e-mails. So what?

1189
01:00:40,380 --> 01:00:41,800
安德森，别说出声来
Anderson, don't talk out loud.

1190
01:00:41,810 --> 01:00:43,310
整条街的智商都被你拉低了
You lower the IQ of the whole street.

1191
01:00:43,320 --> 01:00:44,990
我们远不止能读她的电子邮件
We can do much more than just read her emails.

1192
01:00:45,030 --> 01:00:46,700
这是智能手机，装有GPS
It's a smartphone, it's got GPS.

1193
01:00:47,080 --> 01:00:48,910
意味着如果丢了，你可以在线定位它
Which means if you lose it, you can locate it online.

1194
01:00:48,930 --> 01:00:51,100
她把我们直接引导到杀死她的人
She's leading us directly to the man who killed her.

1195
01:00:51,600 --> 01:00:53,060
- 除非他扔了手机  - 我们知道他没扔
- Unless he got rid of it. - We know he didn't.

1196
01:00:53,540 --> 01:00:54,950
来啊，来啊，快点
Come on, come on. Quickly!

1197
01:00:54,950 --> 01:00:57,550
夏洛克，亲爱的，那位出租司机…
Sherlock, dear. This taxi driver...

1198
01:00:57,610 --> 01:01:00,230
哈德森夫人，你是不是该用晚上的那啥药了
Mrs Hudson, isn't it time for your evening soother?

1199
01:01:01,120 --> 01:01:03,420
准备车，弄架直升机，我们得尽快赶去
Get vehicles, get a helicopter. We have to go as fast as we can.

1200
01:01:03,430 --> 01:01:04,880
这个手机电池不会永远持续
This phone battery won't last for ever.

1201
01:01:04,900 --> 01:01:06,550
我们只有地图上的定位点，没有名字
We'll just have a map reference, not a name.

1202
01:01:06,560 --> 01:01:07,600
这是个开始
It's a start!

1203
01:01:07,750 --> 01:01:08,550
夏洛克
Sherlock...

1204
01:01:08,700 --> 01:01:10,110
缩小范围，不再是伦敦所有人了
Narrows it down from just anyone in London.

1205
01:01:10,120 --> 01:01:12,430
- 这是我们第一个适当的线索  - 夏洛克
- It's the first proper lead we've had. - Sherlock...

1206
01:01:12,520 --> 01:01:14,010
它在哪里？快，哪里？
Where is it? Quickly, where?

1207
01:01:14,330 --> 01:01:17,950
它在…这儿，它在…贝克街221B
It's...here. It's...in 22 1 Baker Street.

1208
01:01:19,960 --> 01:01:21,610
它怎么会在这里？
How can it be here?

1209
01:01:22,300 --> 01:01:23,030
怎么会？
How?

1210
01:01:23,300 --> 01:01:26,110
也许它在箱子里，你带回来的时候就…
Maybe it was in the case when you brought it back and it

1211
01:01:26,720 --> 01:01:27,670
掉到什么地方了
fell out somewhere.

1212
01:01:27,700 --> 01:01:30,100
而我没注意到？我？我没注意到？
And I didn't notice it? Me? I didn't notice?

1213
01:01:30,110 --> 01:01:32,000
不管怎样，我们发了短信，他打回电话了
Anyway, we texted him, and he called back.

1214
01:01:32,400 --> 01:01:35,420
伙计们，我们还要在这里找一部手机
Guys, we're also looking for a mobile somewhere here,

1215
01:01:35,430 --> 01:01:36,210
是死者的物品
belonged to the victim.

1216
01:01:36,220 --> 01:01:39,350
谁是我们不认识也会信任的人？
Who do we trust, even if we don't know them?

1217
01:01:48,120 --> 01:01:50,990
谁去哪里都不引人注意？
Who passes unnoticed wherever they go?

1218
01:01:55,440 --> 01:01:58,030
谁在人群当中狩猎？
Who hunts in the middle of a crowd?

1219
01:02:36,160 --> 01:02:38,000
- 夏洛克，你还好吧？  - 什么？
- Sherlock, are you OK? - What...?

1220
01:02:39,240 --> 01:02:41,190
对对，我没事
Yeah, yeah... I'm fine.

1221
01:02:41,500 --> 01:02:43,320
所以那部手机怎么会在这里？
So, how can the phone be here?

1222
01:02:43,340 --> 01:02:44,390
不知道
Don't know.

1223
01:02:44,600 --> 01:02:46,510
- 我再试试  - 好主意
- I'll try it again. - Good idea.

1224
01:02:46,910 --> 01:02:48,110
你去哪儿？
Where are you going?

1225
01:02:48,200 --> 01:02:50,750
新鲜空气，出去站一会儿，不会太久
Fresh air, just popping outside for a moment. Won't be long.

1226
01:02:51,820 --> 01:02:53,830
- 你确定没事吗？  - 我没事
- Are you sure you're all right? - I'm fine.

1227
01:03:04,280 --> 01:03:05,710
夏洛克·福尔摩斯叫的车
Taxi for Sherlock Holmes.

1228
01:03:09,500 --> 01:03:11,110
我没有叫出租
I didn't order a taxi.

1229
01:03:11,650 --> 01:03:13,310
不代表你不需要一辆
Doesn't mean you don't need one.

1230
01:03:14,680 --> 01:03:16,230
你就是那个的哥
You're the cabbie.

1231
01:03:17,500 --> 01:03:20,110
停在诺森伯兰街外面的那个
The one who stopped outside Northumberland Street.

1232
01:03:24,500 --> 01:03:27,230
是你  不是你的乘客
It was you. Not your passenger.

1233
01:03:27,620 --> 01:03:30,130
瞧，从来没人想过的哥
See? No-one ever thinks about the cabbie.

1234
01:03:30,620 --> 01:03:32,430
就像你隐形了
It's like you're invisible.

1235
01:03:32,840 --> 01:03:34,310
就是个后脑勺而已
Just the back of an 'ead.

1236
01:03:35,320 --> 01:03:37,990
连环杀手的特有优势
Proper advantage for a serial killer.

1237
01:03:40,500 --> 01:03:42,270
- 这是在认罪吗？  - 哦，是的
- Is this a confession? - Oh, yeah.

1238
01:03:43,850 --> 01:03:45,510
我另外再告诉你
I'll tell you what else...

1239
01:03:45,850 --> 01:03:47,670
要是你现在叫警察，我不会跑
If you call the coppers now, I won't run.

1240
01:03:48,730 --> 01:03:51,250
我会好好待着，他们可以拿下我，我保证
I'll sit quiet, and they can take me down, I promise.

1241
01:03:52,500 --> 01:03:53,400
为什么？
Why?

1242
01:03:53,970 --> 01:03:55,210
因为你不会那样做
Cos you're not going to do that.

1243
01:03:55,650 --> 01:03:56,710
我不会吗？
Am I not?

1244
01:03:58,480 --> 01:04:01,470
我没有杀那四个人，福尔摩斯先生
I didn't kill those four people, Mr Holmes.

1245
01:04:01,860 --> 01:04:03,630
我跟他们交谈
I spoke to 'em...

1246
01:04:03,900 --> 01:04:05,790
他们就自杀了
and they killed themselves.

1247
01:04:07,500 --> 01:04:10,510
如果你现在叫警察，我跟你保证一件事
If you get the coppers now, I'll promise you one thing.

1248
01:04:12,080 --> 01:04:14,230
我永远不会告诉你我说了什么
I will never tell you what I said.

1249
01:04:19,920 --> 01:04:21,250
但也再不会有人死了
No-one else will die, though,

1250
01:04:21,260 --> 01:04:22,990
我相信他们接受这结果
and I believe they call that a result.

1251
01:04:23,700 --> 01:04:27,030
而你将永远不会明白那些人怎么死的
And you won't ever understand how those people died.

1252
01:04:28,120 --> 01:04:30,430
你关心的是哪种结果呢？
What kind of result do you care about?

1253
01:04:46,230 --> 01:04:48,110
要是我想要了解
If I wanted to understand...

1254
01:04:49,740 --> 01:04:50,750
我该怎么做？
...what would I do?

1255
01:04:51,160 --> 01:04:52,390
让我载你一程
Let me take you for a ride.

1256
01:04:52,400 --> 01:04:53,590
让你也把我杀了？
So you can kill me too?

1257
01:04:53,640 --> 01:04:55,790
我不想杀你，福尔摩斯先生
I don't want to kill you, Mr Holmes.

1258
01:04:57,500 --> 01:04:58,990
我会跟你谈谈
I'm going to talk to you...

1259
01:05:00,820 --> 01:05:03,400
然后你就会杀死自己
...and then you're going to kill yourself.

1260
01:05:20,900 --> 01:05:21,980
他刚上了一辆出租车
He just got in a cab...

1261
01:05:22,170 --> 01:05:24,510
是夏洛克，他刚坐出租车走了
It's Sherlock. He just drove off in a cab.

1262
01:05:24,520 --> 01:05:26,210
我跟你说过，他常这样
I told you, he does that.

1263
01:05:26,280 --> 01:05:27,730
又特么走了
He bloody left again.

1264
01:05:28,020 --> 01:05:29,410
我们在浪费时间
We're wasting our time!

1265
01:05:29,950 --> 01:05:31,830
我在打那个手机，铃声在响
I'm...calling the phone, it's ringing out.

1266
01:05:43,860 --> 01:05:45,740
既然响铃，它就不在这里
And if it's ringing, it's not here.

1267
01:05:45,750 --> 01:05:47,180
我再试试搜索
I'll try the search again.

1268
01:05:47,210 --> 01:05:49,210
这还重要吗？有半点用吗
Does it matter? Does any of it?

1269
01:05:49,600 --> 01:05:52,000
他就是个疯子 他总是让你失望
He's just a lunatic and he'll always let you down.

1270
01:05:52,010 --> 01:05:55,230
你在浪费时间 我们大家的时间
And you're wasting your time. All our time.

1271
01:06:01,740 --> 01:06:03,670
好了，大家
OK, everybody...

1272
01:06:04,000 --> 01:06:05,230
收工
done here.

1273
01:06:07,900 --> 01:06:09,430
你怎么找到我的？
How did you find me?

1274
01:06:09,720 --> 01:06:11,310
我认出了你
Oh, I recognised you.

1275
01:06:13,120 --> 01:06:14,910
就在我看见你追踪我的车时
Soon as I saw you chasing my cab.

1276
01:06:15,920 --> 01:06:17,990
夏洛克·福尔摩斯
Sherlock Holmes!

1277
01:06:19,240 --> 01:06:20,470
有人跟我警告过你
I was warned about you.

1278
01:06:21,600 --> 01:06:25,310
我也去过你的网站，精彩的东西，爱死了
I've been on your website too. Brilliant stuff! Loved it.

1279
01:06:26,270 --> 01:06:27,590
谁跟你警告过我？
Who warned you about me?

1280
01:06:27,680 --> 01:06:29,700
只是一个注意你的人
Just someone out there who's noticed.

1281
01:06:31,120 --> 01:06:32,190
谁？
Who?

1282
01:06:39,770 --> 01:06:40,990
谁会注意我？
Who would notice me?

1283
01:06:41,500 --> 01:06:44,150
- 你太谦虚了，福尔摩斯先生  - 我真不是
- You're too modest, Mr Holmes. - I'm really not.

1284
01:06:44,800 --> 01:06:46,510
你有个粉丝呢
Got yourself a fan.

1285
01:06:47,600 --> 01:06:48,700
多告诉我一点
Tell me more.

1286
01:06:49,550 --> 01:06:50,910
你只能知道这么多了
That's all you're going to know.

1287
01:06:52,480 --> 01:06:54,030
这辈子里
In this lifetime.

1288
01:06:55,170 --> 01:06:57,750
他为什么那么做？他为什么必须走？
Why did he do that? Why did he have to leave?

1289
01:06:58,500 --> 01:06:59,900
你比我更了解他
You know him better than I do.

1290
01:07:00,450 --> 01:07:03,110
我认识他五年了  但还是不了解他
I've known him for five years and, no, I don't.

1291
01:07:04,800 --> 01:07:06,270
那你为何容忍他？
So why do you put up with him?

1292
01:07:07,130 --> 01:07:09,230
因为我绝望没招了，这就是原因
Because I'm desperate, that's why.

1293
01:07:11,140 --> 01:07:13,870
也因为夏洛克·福尔摩斯是个了不起的人
And because Sherlock Holmes is a great man,

1294
01:07:13,960 --> 01:07:17,590
而且我想，有一天，如果我们非常非常幸运的话
and I think one day, if we're very, very lucky,

1295
01:07:18,060 --> 01:07:19,870
他甚至可能成为个好人
he might even be a good one.

1296
01:07:40,800 --> 01:07:42,270
我们在哪里？
Where are we?

1297
01:07:43,280 --> 01:07:46,700
你知道伦敦的每一条街道  你很清楚我们在哪里
You know every street in London. You know exactly where we are.

1298
01:07:46,800 --> 01:07:49,550
罗兰克尔成人教育学院
Roland-Kerr Further Education College.

1299
01:07:49,970 --> 01:07:52,410
- 为什么来这儿？  - 这儿开着
- Why here? - It's open.

1300
01:07:52,500 --> 01:07:53,770
清洁工在里面
Cleaners are in.

1301
01:07:54,400 --> 01:07:55,870
当的哥有一个好处…
One thing about being a cabbie -

1302
01:07:55,960 --> 01:07:58,650
你总是知道某个僻静理想的杀人地点
you always know a nice quiet spot for a murder.

1303
01:07:58,730 --> 01:08:01,710
我惊讶我们没有更多人拓展这业务
I'm surprised more of us don't branch out.

1304
01:08:02,520 --> 01:08:04,710
你就跟受害者走进去？怎么办到？
And you just walk your victims in? How?

1305
01:08:06,240 --> 01:08:08,230
哦…乏味
Oh... Dull.

1306
01:08:08,420 --> 01:08:09,910
别担心，好戏在后头呢
Don't worry. It gets better.

1307
01:08:10,980 --> 01:08:13,750
你不能用枪逼着人自杀吧
You can't make people take their own lives at gunpoint.

1308
01:08:13,840 --> 01:08:15,190
我没有
I don't.

1309
01:08:15,550 --> 01:08:17,600
比那个强多了
It's much better than that.

1310
01:08:18,210 --> 01:08:21,110
对你不用这个，因为你会跟来
Don't need this with you. Cos you'll follow me.

1311
01:09:13,250 --> 01:09:15,030
你看如何？
Well, what do you think?

1312
01:09:16,520 --> 01:09:17,710
随你喜欢了
It's up to you.

1313
01:09:18,520 --> 01:09:20,110
你是要死在这里的人
You're the one who's going to die here.

1314
01:09:22,500 --> 01:09:23,750
不，我不是
No, I'm not.

1315
01:09:23,900 --> 01:09:25,270
他们都这么说
That's what they all say.

1316
01:09:27,320 --> 01:09:28,830
咱俩聊聊吧？
Shall we talk?

1317
01:09:43,560 --> 01:09:45,150
有点冒险，对吗
Bit risky, wasn't it?

1318
01:09:46,160 --> 01:09:49,070
从半打警察眼皮子底下把我带走
Took me away under the eye of about half a dozen policemen.

1319
01:09:49,320 --> 01:09:51,310
他们没那么蠢
They're not that stupid.

1320
01:09:51,750 --> 01:09:53,630
而且哈德森太太会记得你
And Mrs Hudson will remember you.

1321
01:09:53,720 --> 01:09:56,550
你把这叫做冒险？  不...
You call that a risk? Nah...

1322
01:09:56,800 --> 01:09:58,710
这才叫冒险
This...is a risk.

1323
01:10:06,200 --> 01:10:08,600
哦，我喜欢这一点
Oh, I like this bit.

1324
01:10:09,040 --> 01:10:10,870
因为你还没搞懂，对吧
Cos you don't get it yet, do ya?

1325
01:10:12,800 --> 01:10:14,870
你马上就会明白
But you're about to.

1326
01:10:15,880 --> 01:10:17,550
我只需这样…
I just have to do this...

1327
01:10:23,160 --> 01:10:25,390
没想到这个，对吧
Weren't expecting that, were ya?

1328
01:10:26,400 --> 01:10:27,990
你会喜欢这个的
Oh, you're gonna love this.

1329
01:10:28,080 --> 01:10:31,790
- 喜欢什么？  - 夏洛克·福尔摩斯，看看你
- Love what? - Sherlock Holmes...look at you!

1330
01:10:33,200 --> 01:10:34,680
活生生的在这里
Here in the flesh.

1331
01:10:35,680 --> 01:10:38,500
你那个网站，你的粉丝给我讲了
That website of yours, your fan told me about it.

1332
01:10:38,850 --> 01:10:39,990
我的粉丝？
My fan?

1333
01:10:40,400 --> 01:10:42,150
你那么杰出
You are brilliant.

1334
01:10:42,700 --> 01:10:44,990
你是个特有的天才
You are a proper genius.

1335
01:10:45,700 --> 01:10:48,750
演绎科学，那东西...
The Science Of Deduction. Now, that...

1336
01:10:49,100 --> 01:10:50,800
是特出的想法
is proper thinking.

1337
01:10:52,640 --> 01:10:55,370
我们就来说说，人们为什么不会思考？
Between you and me sitting here, why can't people think?

1338
01:10:56,920 --> 01:10:59,230
这不让你发疯吗？
Don't it make you mad?

1339
01:11:00,110 --> 01:11:02,990
为什么人们就不能思考一下呢
Why can't people just think?

1340
01:11:06,700 --> 01:11:10,350
哦，我明白了，这么说你也是个特有的天才
Oh, I see... So you're a proper genius too.

1341
01:11:10,900 --> 01:11:12,550
看起来不像吧
Don't look it, do I?

1342
01:11:13,560 --> 01:11:15,630
可笑的小男人，开着出租
Funny little man driving a cab.

1343
01:11:16,640 --> 01:11:18,830
不过你马上就能了解更多了
But you'll know better in a minute.

1344
01:11:19,000 --> 01:11:21,910
很大机会 这是你一生所知的最后一件事
Chances are it'll be the last thing you ever know.

1345
01:11:24,070 --> 01:11:26,800
好吧，两个瓶子，解释下
OK, two bottles. Explain.

1346
01:11:27,040 --> 01:11:29,410
一个无毒瓶  一个有毒瓶
There's a good bottle and a bad bottle.

1347
01:11:29,750 --> 01:11:32,110
你拿了无毒瓶里的药丸，你活
You take the pill from the good bottle, you live.

1348
01:11:32,700 --> 01:11:36,230
你拿了有毒瓶里的药丸...你死
You take the pill from the bad bottle...you die.

1349
01:11:36,400 --> 01:11:38,980
- 两个瓶子当然完全一样  - 各个方面
- Both bottles are of course identical. - In every way.

1350
01:11:39,000 --> 01:11:40,990
- 但你知道哪个是哪个  - 我当然知道
- And you know which is which. - Of course I know.

1351
01:11:41,080 --> 01:11:41,930
而我不知道
But I don't.

1352
01:11:41,980 --> 01:11:44,810
你知道就不是游戏了  是你来选
Wouldn't be a game if you knew - you're the one who chooses.

1353
01:11:45,100 --> 01:11:47,000
我为什么要选？我什么也得不到
Why should I? I've got nothing to go on.

1354
01:11:47,700 --> 01:11:48,750
我有什么好处？
What's in it for me?

1355
01:11:49,500 --> 01:11:51,550
我还没告诉你最精彩的部分呢
I haven't told you the best bit yet.

1356
01:11:52,600 --> 01:11:54,400
不管你选哪个瓶子
Whatever bottle you choose,

1357
01:11:54,880 --> 01:11:56,430
我将拿起另一瓶里的药丸
I take the pill from the other one.

1358
01:11:57,420 --> 01:11:58,870
然后  我们一起...
And then together...

1359
01:11:59,480 --> 01:12:01,430
把我们的药吃下去
we take our medicine.

1360
01:12:03,640 --> 01:12:06,470
我不作弊，由你来选
I won't cheat. It's your choice.

1361
01:12:07,760 --> 01:12:10,000
你选剩下哪个药丸我都吃掉
I'll take whatever pill you don't.

1362
01:12:12,720 --> 01:12:15,310
没想到这一手，是吧，福尔摩斯先生？
Didn't expect that, did you, Mr Holmes?

1363
01:12:15,800 --> 01:12:17,630
这就是你对其他人的做法
This is what you did to the rest of them,

1364
01:12:17,720 --> 01:12:20,150
- 你给他们一个选择？ - 现在我给你一个
- you gave them a choice? - And now I'm giving you one.

1365
01:12:21,980 --> 01:12:23,330
你不用着急
You take your time.

1366
01:12:23,900 --> 01:12:25,300
集中精神
Get yourself together.

1367
01:12:26,560 --> 01:12:27,860
我要你尽情游戏
I want your best game.

1368
01:12:27,920 --> 01:12:29,600
这不是游戏，这是机率
It's not a game, it's chance.

1369
01:12:29,610 --> 01:12:32,230
我玩了4次，我还活着
I've played four times. I'm alive.

1370
01:12:33,500 --> 01:12:36,150
这不是机率，福尔摩斯先生，这是下棋
It's not chance, Mr Holmes - it's chess.

1371
01:12:37,720 --> 01:12:40,350
这是一局棋，只走一步
It's a game of chess, with one move...

1372
01:12:41,440 --> 01:12:43,430
一个幸存者
...and one survivor.

1373
01:12:44,800 --> 01:12:47,190
而这…这个…
And this...this...

1374
01:12:47,280 --> 01:12:49,030
就是那一步
is the move.

1375
01:12:57,300 --> 01:13:00,590
我刚给你的是无毒的 还是有毒的瓶子？
Did I just give you the good bottle or the bad bottle?

1376
01:13:00,850 --> 01:13:02,910
你可以选任何一个
You can choose either one.

1377
01:13:05,980 --> 01:13:09,120
不，雷斯垂德探长，我得和他谈谈
No, Detective Inspector Lestrade - I need to speak to him.

1378
01:13:09,230 --> 01:13:11,170
很重要，紧急状况
It's important. It's an emergency.

1379
01:13:11,600 --> 01:13:13,430
呃，这里左转，请你左转
Er, left here, please. Left here...

1380
01:13:25,320 --> 01:13:27,470
你准备好了吗，福尔摩斯先生？
You ready yet, Mr Holmes?

1381
01:13:27,800 --> 01:13:28,810
准备好下棋了吗？
Ready to play?

1382
01:13:28,810 --> 01:13:31,440
下什么？ 这是50比50的机率
Play what? It's a 50:50 chance.

1383
01:13:31,450 --> 01:13:33,950
你不是和数字下，而是和我下
You're not playing the numbers - you're playing me.

1384
01:13:36,680 --> 01:13:39,070
我刚才给你无毒药丸还是有毒药丸呢
Did I just give you the good pill or the bad pill?

1385
01:13:39,500 --> 01:13:41,000
这是诈唬呢？
Is it a bluff

1386
01:13:41,600 --> 01:13:43,000
还是双重诈唬？
or a double bluff?

1387
01:13:43,550 --> 01:13:44,500
还是三重诈唬？
Or a triple bluff?

1388
01:13:44,510 --> 01:13:45,440
仍然不过是机率
It's still just chance.

1389
01:13:45,450 --> 01:13:47,400
连赢四个人？ 这不是机率
Four people, in a row? It's not chance.

1390
01:13:47,410 --> 01:13:49,070
- 运气  - 是天赋
- Luck. - It's genius!

1391
01:13:50,900 --> 01:13:53,000
我知道人们怎么思考
I know how people think.

1392
01:13:53,310 --> 01:13:55,230
我知道人们怎么考虑我的想法
I know how people think I think.

1393
01:13:56,240 --> 01:13:58,830
我能全看透，就像脑子里有一张地图
I can see it all like a map inside my head.

1394
01:13:59,760 --> 01:14:02,650
人人都那么蠢，连你也是
Everyone's so stupid, even you.

1395
01:14:02,970 --> 01:14:04,960
或者，也许上帝就是偏爱我
Or maybe God just loves me.

1396
01:14:08,120 --> 01:14:10,870
不管怎样，你是个浪费生命的的哥
Either way, you're wasted as a cabbie.

1397
01:14:19,600 --> 01:14:21,110
所以….
So...

1398
01:14:22,120 --> 01:14:26,230
你四次冒生命危险，只为杀死陌生人，为什么？
...you risked your life four times just to kill strangers - why?

1399
01:14:26,900 --> 01:14:27,800
该下棋了
Time to play.

1400
01:14:28,150 --> 01:14:31,700
我正在下呢，该我走棋了
Oh, I am playing. This is my turn.

1401
01:14:32,500 --> 01:14:34,620
你的左耳后面有剃须膏沫
There's shaving foam behind your left ear.

1402
01:14:35,010 --> 01:14:36,870
没人给你指出来
Nobody's pointed it out to you.

1403
01:14:36,960 --> 01:14:38,420
痕迹说明以前也有过
Traces of where it's happened before,

1404
01:14:38,500 --> 01:14:41,210
所以明显你是一个人住，没人告诉你
so obviously you live on your own there's no-one to tell you.

1405
01:14:41,220 --> 01:14:42,720
但还有一张孩子们的照片
But there's a photograph of children.

1406
01:14:42,730 --> 01:14:44,510
孩子们的母亲却从照片里裁掉了
The children's mother's been cut out of the picture

1407
01:14:44,520 --> 01:14:46,310
如果她死了，那还会留在里面
If she'd died, she'd still be there.

1408
01:14:46,480 --> 01:14:48,350
照片是旧的，但相框很新
The photograph's old, but the frame's new.

1409
01:14:48,360 --> 01:14:50,710
你想念你的孩子们，却无法见到他们
You think of your children, but you don't get to see them.

1410
01:14:50,800 --> 01:14:52,990
分居的父亲
Estranged father.

1411
01:14:53,080 --> 01:14:54,870
她带走了孩子
She took the kids,

1412
01:14:55,030 --> 01:14:58,130
但你仍然爱他们，仍然心痛
but you still love them, and it still hurts.

1413
01:14:59,750 --> 01:15:00,750
哦，还有呢
Ah, but there's more.

1414
01:15:02,600 --> 01:15:04,630
你的衣服，最近才洗过
Your clothes. Recently laundered,

1415
01:15:04,720 --> 01:15:07,630
但你穿的每一样东西，至少有3年那么旧
but everything you're wearing is at least...three years old?

1416
01:15:07,900 --> 01:15:11,350
保留现状 但对前途无计划
Keeping up appearances, but not planning ahead.

1417
01:15:12,360 --> 01:15:16,350
而你又在这里搞神风谋杀，这是为何？
And here you are on a kamikaze murder spree. What's that about?

1418
01:15:20,680 --> 01:15:24,990
哦，三年前…他们是那时候告诉你的吧？
three years ago. Is that when they told you?

1419
01:15:25,000 --> 01:15:27,190
告诉我什么？
Told me what?

1420
01:15:27,280 --> 01:15:29,440
- 说你是将死之人  - 你也是
- That you're a dead man walking. - So are you.

1421
01:15:29,500 --> 01:15:32,050
反正你时日不多了，我说得对吗？
You don't have long, though. Am I right?

1422
01:15:34,080 --> 01:15:36,510
动脉瘤  就在这里面
Aneurism. Right in 'ere.

1423
01:15:39,220 --> 01:15:42,000
任何一口气都可能是我最后一口
Any breath could be my last.

1424
01:15:42,700 --> 01:15:45,730
就因为你要死了，你就连杀四个人
And because you're dying, you've just murdered four people.

1425
01:15:45,740 --> 01:15:47,710
我可比那四个人活得久
I've outlived four people.

1426
01:15:49,600 --> 01:15:52,150
对于得动脉瘤的人，那可是最高兴的事了
That's the most fun you can have with an aneurism.

1427
01:15:53,200 --> 01:15:56,710
不...不 还有别的
No... No, there's something else.

1428
01:15:56,800 --> 01:15:58,950
你不会因为痛苦而杀四个人
You didn't just kill four people because you're bitter.

1429
01:15:58,960 --> 01:16:00,750
痛苦是一种麻痹
Bitterness is a paralytic.

1430
01:16:01,370 --> 01:16:04,790
爱才是更为歹毒的动力
Love is a much more vicious motivator.

1431
01:16:06,400 --> 01:16:09,250
这和你的孩子有某种关联
Somehow, this is about your children.

1432
01:16:12,970 --> 01:16:15,350
- 你厉害  - 但怎么关联呢
- You are good, in't ya? - But how?

1433
01:16:16,800 --> 01:16:19,590
等我死了，他们得不到多少，我的孩子们
When I die, they won't get much, my kids.

1434
01:16:21,880 --> 01:16:23,960
开出租车赚不了多少钱
Not a lot of money in driving cabs.

1435
01:16:23,970 --> 01:16:25,170
连环杀人也没有
Or serial killing.

1436
01:16:25,180 --> 01:16:26,330
你会吃惊的
You'd be surprised.

1437
01:16:26,780 --> 01:16:28,010
那就惊惊我
Surprise me.

1438
01:16:30,400 --> 01:16:31,900
我有个赞助商
I have a sponsor.

1439
01:16:32,800 --> 01:16:33,850
你有什么？
You have a what?

1440
01:16:33,860 --> 01:16:36,870
我每取一条命，就有一笔钱给我的孩子
For every life I take, money goes to my kids.

1441
01:16:37,400 --> 01:16:40,700
我杀得越多…他们就越宽裕
The more I kill... the better off they'll be.

1442
01:16:42,040 --> 01:16:44,830
看吧  比你想象的好得多
You see? It's nicer than you think.

1443
01:16:44,840 --> 01:16:46,390
有谁会赞助一个连环杀手？
Who'd sponsor a serial killer?

1444
01:16:46,480 --> 01:16:49,110
谁会是夏洛克·福尔摩斯的粉丝？
Who'd be a fan of Sherlock Holmes?

1445
01:16:52,070 --> 01:16:55,430
你不是唯一欣赏高明谋杀的人
You're not the only one to enjoy a good murder.

1446
01:16:56,020 --> 01:16:57,850
外面还有一些人 跟你一样
There's others out there just like you,

1447
01:16:57,850 --> 01:16:59,630
不过你只是一介凡人
except you're just a man.

1448
01:17:01,040 --> 01:17:03,270
而他们却远不止如此
And they're so much more than that.

1449
01:17:05,320 --> 01:17:06,710
什么意思…
What do you mean...

1450
01:17:06,900 --> 01:17:08,870
不止是一个人？
more than a man?

1451
01:17:09,970 --> 01:17:11,960
一个组织…什么？
An organisation...what?

1452
01:17:12,570 --> 01:17:14,900
有一个名字，没人说出来
There's a name that no-one says.

1453
01:17:16,200 --> 01:17:17,990
我也不会说的
And I'm not going to say it either.

1454
01:17:19,560 --> 01:17:21,790
现在，闲聊够了
Now, enough chatter.

1455
01:17:23,950 --> 01:17:25,550
该选择了
Time to choose.

1456
01:17:30,220 --> 01:17:31,270
夏洛克
Sherlock!

1457
01:17:36,470 --> 01:17:37,050
夏洛克
Sherlock!

1458
01:17:38,000 --> 01:17:41,430
要是我两个都不选呢？我可以直接走人
What if I don't choose either? I could just walk out of here.

1459
01:17:44,960 --> 01:17:47,350
你可以选50%的机会
You can take a 50:50 chance,

1460
01:17:48,100 --> 01:17:50,390
或让我射爆你的头
or I can shoot you in the head.

1461
01:17:51,760 --> 01:17:53,130
够好笑的
Funnily enough,

1462
01:17:53,480 --> 01:17:55,310
至今没人选这个选项
no-one's ever gone for that option.

1463
01:17:55,750 --> 01:17:57,470
那我选枪 请吧
I'll have the gun, please.

1464
01:17:58,760 --> 01:18:00,110
你确定吗？
Are you sure?

1465
01:18:01,160 --> 01:18:03,790
肯定的  就选枪
Definitely. The gun.

1466
01:18:04,410 --> 01:18:05,950
你不想给朋友打个电话？
You don't want to phone a friend

1467
01:18:07,300 --> 01:18:09,010
选枪
The gun.

1468
01:18:14,180 --> 01:18:15,990
看见真枪我认得出来
I know a real gun when I see one.

1469
01:18:17,880 --> 01:18:20,150
- 其他人都没发现  - 无疑
- None of the others did. - Clearly.

1470
01:18:21,200 --> 01:18:24,550
好了，这一切非常有趣
Well, this has been very interesting.

1471
01:18:25,240 --> 01:18:27,150
期待法庭上见
I look forward to the court case.

1472
01:18:30,750 --> 01:18:33,150
你走之前，问一下你想清楚了吗？
Just before you go, did you figure it out?

1473
01:18:34,900 --> 01:18:36,470
哪一瓶是无毒的？
Which one's the good bottle?

1474
01:18:36,560 --> 01:18:38,910
当然，小孩把戏
Course. Child's play.

1475
01:18:39,720 --> 01:18:40,990
那是哪一个呢？
Well, which one, then?

1476
01:18:42,600 --> 01:18:44,040
你会挑哪个呢？
Which one would you have picked?

1477
01:18:44,050 --> 01:18:46,190
我只想知道自己能否打败你
Just so I know whether I could have beaten you.

1478
01:18:48,240 --> 01:18:50,070
来吧
Come on!

1479
01:18:50,160 --> 01:18:51,950
开始游戏吧
Play the game.

1480
01:19:07,950 --> 01:19:08,980
有意思
Oh! Interesting.

1481
01:19:18,160 --> 01:19:20,070
你怎么想？
So what do you think?

1482
01:19:21,220 --> 01:19:23,050
来吧？
Shall we?

1483
01:19:25,160 --> 01:19:28,190
真的  你怎么想的？
Really...what do you think?

1484
01:19:29,600 --> 01:19:30,830
你能打败我吗？
Can you beat me?

1485
01:19:33,200 --> 01:19:35,030
你是否够聪明
Are you clever enough...

1486
01:19:36,650 --> 01:19:37,950
可以赌上性命？
to bet your life?

1487
01:19:50,080 --> 01:19:51,270
夏洛克
Sherlock!

1488
01:19:53,620 --> 01:19:55,590
我打赌你很无聊  不是吗
I bet you get bored, don't you?

1489
01:19:56,800 --> 01:19:58,470
我知道你无聊
I know you do.

1490
01:19:59,080 --> 01:20:02,180
你这样的人 如此聪明
A man like you. So clever.

1491
01:20:03,790 --> 01:20:06,810
但若不能证明，聪明又有何意义呢？
But what's the point of being clever if you can't prove it?

1492
01:20:08,680 --> 01:20:10,470
仍旧是瘾君子
Still the addict.

1493
01:20:12,120 --> 01:20:15,830
但这个 这才是真正让你上瘾的东西
But this...this is what you're really addicted to.

1494
01:20:18,000 --> 01:20:19,150
你定会竭尽全力
You'll do anything...

1495
01:20:20,640 --> 01:20:24,450
全力以赴，避免无聊
...anything at all, to stop being bored.

1496
01:20:26,500 --> 01:20:28,150
你现在不无聊了，对吧？
You're not bored now, are ya?

1497
01:20:29,800 --> 01:20:31,000
这不错吧
Isn't it good?

1498
01:20:45,800 --> 01:20:47,190
我对了吗？
Was I right?

1499
01:20:47,280 --> 01:20:48,950
我对了，是吧？
I was, wasn't I?

1500
01:20:49,120 --> 01:20:50,430
我刚才挑对了吗？
Did I get it right?

1501
01:20:54,200 --> 01:20:57,190
好吧  那就告诉我
OK...tell me this.

1502
01:20:58,480 --> 01:21:00,910
你的赞助者，他是谁？
Your sponsor. Who was it?

1503
01:21:01,200 --> 01:21:02,990
那个跟你提起我的人  我的粉丝
The one who told you about me, my fan.

1504
01:21:03,500 --> 01:21:04,870
我要名字
I want a name.

1505
01:21:05,030 --> 01:21:06,390
不
No...

1506
01:21:07,010 --> 01:21:09,550
你要死了，但还有时间折磨你
You're dying, but there's still time to hurt you.

1507
01:21:09,860 --> 01:21:12,230
给我…名字
Give me...A name.

1508
01:21:15,000 --> 01:21:17,750
名字  快说
A name! Now!

1509
01:21:19,680 --> 01:21:20,910
名字
The name!

1510
01:21:21,000 --> 01:21:24,670
莫里亚蒂
Moriarty!

1511
01:21:46,690 --> 01:21:47,820
为什么给我毛毯？
Why have I got this blanket?

1512
01:21:47,830 --> 01:21:49,120
他们老是给我披这条毛毯
They keep putting this blanket on me.

1513
01:21:49,130 --> 01:21:50,680
- 对，为防你受惊吓  - 我没有受惊
- Yeah, it's for shock. - I'm not in shock.

1514
01:21:51,500 --> 01:21:53,510
对，但有人要拍照片
Yeah, but some of the guys want to take photographs.

1515
01:21:55,850 --> 01:21:57,090
那个枪手，没有迹象吗？
So, the shooter - no sign?

1516
01:21:57,480 --> 01:21:59,040
我们赶到前就消失了
Cleared off before we got here.

1517
01:21:59,220 --> 01:22:01,200
不过我料想那种人会有很多敌人
But a guy like that would have had enemies, I suppose.

1518
01:22:01,230 --> 01:22:03,080
其中有人可能正在追杀他 不过
One of them could have been following him, but...

1519
01:22:04,280 --> 01:22:06,030
我们现在毫无头绪
we've got nothing to go on.

1520
01:22:06,480 --> 01:22:08,070
哦，我可不这么想
Oh, I wouldn't say that.

1521
01:22:09,720 --> 01:22:11,150
那好，告诉我
OK. Give me.

1522
01:22:11,660 --> 01:22:14,150
他们从墙上挖出的子弹，来自手枪
The bullet they just dug out of the wall's from a handgun.

1523
01:22:14,480 --> 01:22:16,530
那种距离外的致命一击，从那种武器发射
A kill shot over that distance, from that kind of a weapon,

1524
01:22:16,540 --> 01:22:19,310
那一枪很出色，你们要找的不单是个神枪手，是个战士
that's a crack shot. You're looking for not just a marksman, a fighter.

1525
01:22:19,320 --> 01:22:20,710
他的手必须纹丝不动
His hands couldn't have shaken at all,

1526
01:22:20,720 --> 01:22:22,260
所以很清楚他习惯于暴力
so clearly he's acclimatised to violence.

1527
01:22:22,750 --> 01:22:24,620
然而他等到我面临直接危险才开火
He didn't fire until I was in immediate danger, though

1528
01:22:24,630 --> 01:22:25,940
很强的道德原则
so strong moral principle.

1529
01:22:26,800 --> 01:22:27,620
你找的这人
You're looking for a man

1530
01:22:27,630 --> 01:22:30,350
或许有军队服役的历史 以及...
probably with a history of military service and...

1531
01:22:30,800 --> 01:22:31,910
钢铁般的神经
nerves of steel...

1532
01:22:38,400 --> 01:22:40,030
其实 你猜怎么？ 别管我说的
Actually, do you know what? Ignore me.

1533
01:22:40,040 --> 01:22:41,920
- 啥？  - 别管那些话
- Sorry? - Ignore all of that.

1534
01:22:41,930 --> 01:22:45,110
- 那只是…受惊后的胡说  - 你去哪儿？
- It's just the, er...the shock talking. - Where are you going?

1535
01:22:45,140 --> 01:22:47,140
我得去聊聊租金
I just need to...talk about the...the rent.

1536
01:22:47,150 --> 01:22:49,540
- 我还有几个问题呢  - 现在吗  我受惊了
- I've still got questions. - Oh, what now?! I'm in shock

1537
01:22:49,580 --> 01:22:50,630
你看，我披着毛毯呢
look, I've got a blanket.

1538
01:22:50,720 --> 01:22:51,910
- 夏洛克  - 而且
- Sherlock! - And...

1539
01:22:52,000 --> 01:22:53,950
我刚帮你抓了连环杀手
I just caught you a serial killer...

1540
01:22:55,020 --> 01:22:56,050
多多少少吧
more or less.

1541
01:22:58,640 --> 01:23:01,990
好吧，我们明天找你，你走吧
OK. We'll pull you in tomorrow. Off you go.

1542
01:23:09,540 --> 01:23:12,470
嗯，多诺万警佐，刚才解释了…
Erm...Sergeant Donovan's...just been explaining...

1543
01:23:12,470 --> 01:23:15,000
所有事情，两颗药丸…
everything. Two pills...

1544
01:23:16,160 --> 01:23:18,310
吓人的事，对吧？ 吓人
Dreadful business, isn't it? Dreadful.

1545
01:23:19,350 --> 01:23:20,520
好枪法
Good shot.

1546
01:23:21,720 --> 01:23:23,790
对对，一定是的，穿过窗户
Yes. Yes, must have been. Through that window.

1547
01:23:23,880 --> 01:23:25,800
你清楚
Well, you'd know.

1548
01:23:27,440 --> 01:23:29,150
得把你手指上的火药灼痕去掉
Need to get the powder burns out of your fingers.

1549
01:23:29,240 --> 01:23:30,590
我认为你不会因此坐牢
I don't suppose you'd serve time for this,

1550
01:23:30,600 --> 01:23:31,730
但我们还是避免上庭吧
but let's avoid the court case.

1551
01:23:33,950 --> 01:23:36,030
- 你没事吧  - 对，我当然没事
- Are you all right? - Yes, of course I'm all right.

1552
01:23:36,120 --> 01:23:37,830
- 你刚杀了人  - 是的，我...
- Well, you have just killed a man. - Yes, I...

1553
01:23:41,560 --> 01:23:42,870
那倒是，对吧
That's true, isn't it?

1554
01:23:44,180 --> 01:23:46,190
不过他不是个很好的人
But he wasn't a very nice man.

1555
01:23:47,840 --> 01:23:49,630
是呀，他真不算好人，不是吗
No. No, he wasn't, really, was he?

1556
01:23:49,640 --> 01:23:51,550
说白了就是个坏透了的的哥
Frankly, a bloody awful cabbie.

1557
01:23:52,750 --> 01:23:54,610
那倒是，他是个坏的哥
That's true, he was a bad cabbie.

1558
01:23:54,900 --> 01:23:57,230
你该看看他带我们兜了多少路到这里
You should have seen the route he took us to get here.

1559
01:23:57,320 --> 01:24:00,140
别闹，我们不能笑 这是罪案现场，别闹
Stop! We can't giggle, it's a crime scene. Stop it.

1560
01:24:00,150 --> 01:24:02,470
- 是你开的枪  - 你声音小点
- You're the one who shot him. - Keep your voice down!

1561
01:24:02,560 --> 01:24:06,030
- 抱歉  他是太紧张了  - 抱歉
- Sorry, it's just, erm...nerves, I think. - Sorry.

1562
01:24:06,740 --> 01:24:09,000
你不会真要吞那该死的药片，对吧？
You were going to take that damn pill, weren't you?

1563
01:24:09,010 --> 01:24:10,310
当然不会
Course I wasn't.

1564
01:24:11,010 --> 01:24:13,310
拖延时间而已，知道你会出现
Biding my time. Knew you'd turn up.

1565
01:24:14,100 --> 01:24:14,950
不，你不知道
No, you didn't.

1566
01:24:15,800 --> 01:24:16,910
你就是这么找刺激的，对吧
That's how you get your kicks, isn't it?

1567
01:24:16,920 --> 01:24:18,710
冒生命危险证明自己聪明
You risk your life to prove you're clever.

1568
01:24:18,830 --> 01:24:20,010
我干嘛这么做？
Why would I do that?

1569
01:24:20,220 --> 01:24:21,610
因为你是个笨蛋
Because you're an idiot.

1570
01:24:23,600 --> 01:24:25,790
- 晚饭？  - 饿死了
- Dinner? - Starving.

1571
01:24:26,230 --> 01:24:28,670
贝克街尽头，有家不错的中餐馆，开到凌晨两点
End of Baker Street, there's a good Chinese. Stays open till two.

1572
01:24:28,900 --> 01:24:31,360
中餐馆的好坏能从门把底部三分之一看出来
You can tell a good Chinese by the bottom third of the door handle.

1573
01:24:31,370 --> 01:24:35,110
夏洛克，是他，我跟你提过的那个人
Sherlock...that's him, that's the man I was talking to you about.

1574
01:24:35,360 --> 01:24:37,000
我很清楚他是谁
I know exactly who that is.

1575
01:24:37,960 --> 01:24:40,270
好啊…又破了一个案件？
So...another case cracked.

1576
01:24:40,650 --> 01:24:42,790
多么热心公益呀
How very public-spirited.

1577
01:24:42,880 --> 01:24:45,500
虽然那不是你真实的动机，对吧
Though that's never really your motivation, is it?

1578
01:24:46,150 --> 01:24:47,530
你来这里干嘛？
What are you doing here?

1579
01:24:47,650 --> 01:24:49,390
一如既往，我关心你
As ever, I'm concerned about you.

1580
01:24:49,480 --> 01:24:51,790
对，我已经听到你的“关心”了
Yes, I've been hearing about your "Concern".

1581
01:24:52,030 --> 01:24:53,510
总是如此咄咄逼人
Always so aggressive.

1582
01:24:53,700 --> 01:24:56,530
你从没想过你我是一边的吗？
Did it never occur to you that you and I belong on the same side?

1583
01:24:56,900 --> 01:24:58,510
说来奇怪…没有
Oddly enough...no.

1584
01:24:58,800 --> 01:25:01,590
我们的共同点比你愿意相信的要多
We have more in common than you'd like to believe.

1585
01:25:01,860 --> 01:25:04,570
咱们之间的这点不和 只不过是孩子气
This petty feud between us is simply childish.

1586
01:25:04,590 --> 01:25:05,900
有人会因此难受
People will suffer.

1587
01:25:06,490 --> 01:25:08,550
你知道这总是让老妈烦心
And you know how it always upset Mummy.

1588
01:25:09,800 --> 01:25:11,270
我让她烦心？
I upset her?

1589
01:25:11,550 --> 01:25:13,590
我？
Me?

1590
01:25:13,680 --> 01:25:15,950
让她烦心的不是我，麦克罗夫特
It wasn't me that upset her, Mycroft.

1591
01:25:16,040 --> 01:25:17,450
不 不  等等
No. No, wait...

1592
01:25:17,800 --> 01:25:18,750
老妈？谁的老妈？
Mummy? Who's Mummy?

1593
01:25:18,840 --> 01:25:20,750
母亲，我们的母亲
Mother. Our mother.

1594
01:25:21,280 --> 01:25:23,000
这是我哥哥，麦克罗夫特
This is my brother, Mycroft.

1595
01:25:23,900 --> 01:25:24,870
又发福了
Putting on weight again?

1596
01:25:25,880 --> 01:25:28,270
- 实际上，减肥了  - 他是你哥？
- Losing it, in fact. - He's your brother?

1597
01:25:28,360 --> 01:25:30,230
当然是我哥
Course he's my brother.

1598
01:25:31,240 --> 01:25:32,750
- 那他不是…  - 不是什么？
- So he's not... - Not what?

1599
01:25:34,280 --> 01:25:36,530
不知道…犯罪主脑？
I don't know...criminal mastermind?

1600
01:25:37,900 --> 01:25:38,870
也差不多
Close enough.

1601
01:25:38,880 --> 01:25:39,950
老天爷呀
For goodness' sake,

1602
01:25:40,470 --> 01:25:43,030
我在英国政府里官居末职
I occupy a minor position in the British Government.

1603
01:25:43,100 --> 01:25:44,120
他就是英国政府
He is the British Government,

1604
01:25:44,190 --> 01:25:47,920
当他不忙于英国秘密机构或中情局的副业时
when he's not too busy being the British Secret Service or the CIA on a freelance basis.

1605
01:25:49,000 --> 01:25:50,220
晚安，麦克罗夫特
Good evening, Mycroft.

1606
01:25:50,630 --> 01:25:52,500
尽量别在我到家之前发动一场战争
Try not to start a war before I get home

1607
01:25:52,510 --> 01:25:53,700
你知道那对交通有何影响的
you know what it does for the traffic.

1608
01:25:57,110 --> 01:25:59,000
所以，你说关心他的时候
So, when you say you're concerned about him,

1609
01:25:59,200 --> 01:26:00,280
你是真的关心他？
you actually are concerned?

1610
01:26:00,840 --> 01:26:01,870
是啊，当然
Yes, of course.

1611
01:26:02,880 --> 01:26:04,750
真是小孩子的不和吗？
It actually is a childish feud?

1612
01:26:05,720 --> 01:26:07,340
他一向如此愤愤不平
He's always been so resentful.

1613
01:26:08,160 --> 01:26:09,590
你可以想象圣诞晚餐的情形
You can imagine the Christmas dinners.

1614
01:26:10,500 --> 01:26:11,390
是啊
Yeah

1615
01:26:11,540 --> 01:26:12,490
不，天，不能
No... God, no.

1616
01:26:14,640 --> 01:26:17,550
我最好还是…又见面了
I'd better, erm... Hello again.

1617
01:26:18,960 --> 01:26:21,500
- 你好  - 我们今晚早些时候见过
- Hello. - We met earlier on this evening.

1618
01:26:23,660 --> 01:26:26,630
- 那好，晚安  - 晚安，华生医生
- OK. Good night. - Good night, Dr Watson.

1619
01:26:28,860 --> 01:26:30,440
走  吃点心去
So, dim sum.Mmm!

1620
01:26:30,500 --> 01:26:32,180
我总能猜到幸运饼写什么
I can always predict the fortune cookies.

1621
01:26:32,220 --> 01:26:33,340
- 不，不可能  - 差不多
- No, you can't. - Almost can.

1622
01:26:33,350 --> 01:26:34,870
不过你真中过枪
You did get shot, though.

1623
01:26:34,900 --> 01:26:37,140
- 什么？  - 在阿富汗  真的受过枪伤
- Sorry? - In Afghanistan. There was an actual wound.

1624
01:26:37,150 --> 01:26:39,670
- 哦对，肩膀上  - 肩膀，我就知道
- Oh. Yeah, shoulder. - Shoulder! I thought so.

1625
01:26:39,680 --> 01:26:41,040
- 不你不知道  - 左肩
- No, you didn't. - The left one.

1626
01:26:41,050 --> 01:26:42,870
- 瞎猜中的  - 我从不瞎猜
- Lucky guess. - I never guess.

1627
01:26:42,880 --> 01:26:44,350
你就是猜的
Yes, you do.

1628
01:26:44,440 --> 01:26:46,990
- 你干嘛这么乐？  - 莫里亚蒂
- What are you so happy about? - Moriarty.

1629
01:26:47,080 --> 01:26:50,270
- 莫里亚蒂是什么？  - 一无所知
- What's Moriarty? - I've absolutely no idea.

1630
01:26:52,000 --> 01:26:53,470
长官，可以走了吗？
Sir, shall we go?

1631
01:26:54,560 --> 01:26:57,190
有意思，那个当兵的
Interesting, that soldier fellow.

1632
01:26:57,560 --> 01:26:59,300
他可能造就我弟弟
He could be the making of my brother...

1633
01:27:00,280 --> 01:27:01,710
也可能让他更加无可救药
or make him worse than ever.

1634
01:27:02,760 --> 01:27:06,300
无论哪种，我们最好提高他们的监控级别
Either way, we'd better upgrade their surveillance status.

1635
01:27:06,420 --> 01:27:08,270
启动三级预案
Grade 3 active.

1636
01:27:08,300 --> 01:27:10,150
抱歉长官，对谁的监控级别？
Sorry, sir - whose status?

1637
01:27:12,300 --> 01:27:15,210
夏洛克·福尔摩斯，还有华生医生
Sherlock Holmes and Dr Watson.

